casebody.data:
STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Ramon HERNANDEZ-MENDOZA, Defendant-Appellant. No. 18-0083 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed May 1, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Ramon Hernandez-Mendoza appeals his convictions and sentence for homicide by vehicle, controlled substance violations, and supplying alcohol to minors. CONVICTIONS AFFIRMED, SENTENCE VACATED IN PART, AND REMANDED FOR RESENTENCING.

CONVICTIONS AFFIRMED, SENTENCES VACATED IN PART. REMANDED FOR RESENTENCING.
